{"tid":1103141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大粒墨認罪］台灣少女被殺案 男友認洗黑錢候判 警誡下承認殺人","createTime":"2019-04-12T08:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T12:35:04.000Z","uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbd27ad37a794b77c47d4b922be1f0f93ad24cb","tid":1103141,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e949bb9eed9b8583cb41f24b3c4aa37599824fb7","tid":1103141,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"嚴刑迫供<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272420bbe17c9bfdb159d4e3717a7d642c097db4","tid":1103141,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"少女潘曉穎在台灣被殺，男友陳同佳涉返港後盜用她的信用卡提款逾1.9萬元，並藏有其財物，被警方拘捕。案件去年3月首度在觀塘法院提堂，陳共被控四項洗黑錢罪及三項盜竊交替控罪，並轉介至高等法院。案件今午在高院提訊，由法官彭寶琴審理。庭上透露，陳同佳早於去年12月31日已在東區裁判法院承認四項洗黑錢罪，控方今讀出案情，透露陳在警誡下承認殺人。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時，僅指希望法庭考慮被告沒有案底，並承認罪行，且由去年3月起一直還押至今。除此之外，沒有其他求情。彭官將案件押後至4月29日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n報稱學生的20歲被告陳同佳，原被控兩項盜竊罪及一項處理贓物罪，指他去年2月21至23日間某天，於鑽石山荷里活廣場的恒生銀行櫃員機，分兩次盜取潘10,000元及8,500元；另於3月13日被捕當天，處理潘的匯豐銀行提款卡、Casio數碼相機、iPhone 6手機及20,000元新台幣。<br />\n<br />\n去年7月案件第四度提堂時，控方申請修改處理贓物罪日期，並將盜竊罪由兩項變為三項，指陳分別盜取匯豐10,500、8,500及200元。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後被告第五度解上法庭，控方再提出修訂及新增控罪。其中一項洗黑錢罪指，陳去年2月17至3月13日處理上述潘的財物。另外三罪則指他去年2月19至21日，處理屬匯豐的1.92萬元。至於三項盜竊交替控罪，即涉及匯豐的1.92萬元。"},{"pid":"95cdbeb461eb6df6e80ab6e6f462167d22368fa5","tid":1103141,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"激動得濟打錯， 唔係認罪 係承認殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637925e2fb088ac22ed25bf9a6badafd62e2dddc","tid":1103141,"uid":33352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢係台灣㩒埋錢返香港<br />\n<br />\n係咪完全無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958ba4b52740b7bd12d0ec9709e098cedb6944c4","tid":1103141,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"認又點<br />\n都告唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7875fa83bbe6d86153f31883fc515f0ae5b293fe","tid":1103141,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢可以判三年，符合逃犯引導條例咩？"},{"pid":"93b6f6cec25e9b1b0b5006ab1d533c55d3b58a00","tid":1103141,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗陳庭佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4b2ed15432f3ed50166d7ece94edd8ab975fcf","tid":1103141,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"點解係洗黑錢，而唔係盜取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b13e67dc1af101c3885804016796791ceec732","tid":1103141,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"637925e2fb088ac22ed25bf9a6badafd62e2dddc","tid":1103141,"uid":33352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢係台灣㩒埋錢返香港<br />\n<br />\n係咪完全無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"係 因為犯罪地點係台灣"},{"pid":"d6f689ab7e7b908d33ea5d094afa98391aae163a","tid":1103141,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"晒撚氣，佢認又點，你係香港都唔可以告佢殺人，29號咪可以當庭釋放囉，著草去其他國家囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ff39031177879930b57da773b5df9468c76b41","tid":1103141,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f689